---
import { Image } from '@astrojs/image/components';
import aboutMe from '../assets/images/aboutMe.jpeg';
---

<section data-testid="about" id="about" class="h-[90vh] grid place-content-center">
	<div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-center lg:mb-10">
		<h2 class="font-monospace text-2xl text-shadow dark:text-faint lg:text-4xl">About me</h2>
		<span class="mb-6 ml-2 h-1 w-10 bg-shadow dark:bg-faint"></span>
	</div>
	<section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2">
		<figure class="mx-4 hidden lg:block">
			<Image class:list={`w-full rounded-3xl shadow-lg`} src={aboutMe} alt="SetUp" format="png" width={500} height={400} aspectRatio="16:9" />
		</figure>
		<div class="w-full px-4 text-darkness dark:text-light">
			<p class="mb-6">
				As a <span class="font-extrabold">Frontend Web Developer</span>, my passion lies in creating
				exceptional digital experiences that captivate users. My skills are centered around
				essential languages like JavaScript and TypeScript, and my experience spans a variety of
				cutting-edge technologies such as <span class="font-extrabold">Next.js, React, Astro</span>,
				and <span class="font-extrabold">Svelte</span>. These tools enable me to develop attractive
				and highly functional interfaces.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-6">
				My collaborative approach is evidenced by my ability to seamlessly integrate into
				multidisciplinary teams, where I contribute creative solutions that merge design and
				functionality. My perspective is that of a perpetual learner, always ready to take on new
				challenges and add value to high-quality projects.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-6">
				I am excited about the infinite possibilities that the world of web development has to
				offer, and I eagerly look forward to being part of projects that make a difference in the
				digital experience.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</section>
